-- Croatia's Crodux to Buy Dioki Chemical Maker: Poslovni
-- B y   J a s m i n a   K u z m a n o v i c
-- 2012-12-17T07:27:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-17/croatia-s-crodux-to-buy-dioki-chemical-maker-poslovni.html
Crodux Plin d.o.o., a gas and oil
retailer in  Croatia , plans to buy chemical maker Dioki d.d.,
 Poslovni Dnevnik  reported, citing Crodux owner Ivan Cermak.  Dioki is in bankruptcy procedure and has stopped production
in 2011, Poslovni said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jasmina Kuzmanovic in Zagreb at 
 jkuzmanovic@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  